mName":"Basis for recommendation","depth":3,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field 5fd7702d-64bb-4976-bdd4-a513c7d5a373 --><h3>Basis for recommendation</h3><!-- end field 5fd7702d-64bb-4976-bdd4-a513c7d5a373 -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item b1f2a6ed-cabb-478c-a09d-89921d09749c --><!-- begin field bcece077-b26f-4ea1-b345-27a93aba5f94 --><p>The information on the differential diagnosis of glandular fever is based on expert opinion in review articles [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/glandular-fever-infectious-mononucleosis/references/\">Ebell, 2004</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/glandular-fever-infectious-mononucleosis/references/\">BMJ, 2018</a>] and textbooks [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/glandular-fever-infectious-mononucleosis/references/\">Litman, 2006</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/glandular-fever-infectious-mononucleosis/references/\">Straus, 2006</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/glandular-fever-infectious-mononucleosis/references/\">Johannsen, 2009</a>].</p><!-- end field bcece077-b26f-4ea1-b345-27a93aba5f94 --><!-- end item b1f2a6ed-cabb-478c-a09d-89921d09749c -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}